Vladimir Nabokov

TO: PASCAL COVICI

CC, 1 p.





Goldwin Smith Hall

Itnaca, N.Y.

February 3, 1958

Dear Mr. Covici,

My husband asks me to thank you for sending him the Stanislaus Joyce book.1 He found in it some very interesting information and is very happy to possess it in his library.

